717970f-a.title: Manhattan: Cabrini Boulevard - 186th Street (West)
717970f-a.text:
Vabrini Boulevard, (formerly Northern Avenue) west
side, north from a point to the south of Chittenden Place
(W. 18'th Street) and showing a row of apartments that be-
ain at the N.W. corner of that point. At the left is a
corner of Dr. Chas. V. Paterno's manorial estate and upon
which an apartment proiect is takinm shape, necessitating
derolition of the aforerentioed i-edividuals castle-like
home. Chitteoden Place normally runs parallel to the boulevard
but here it has absorbed that short street that foins both
thoroughfares.
August 2S, 1938.
P.L. Sperr
